🕷️ Web Scraper Bot using Python — Notes
📌 1. What is Web Scraping?
Web scraping is the process of extracting data from websites automatically.
Used to collect large amounts of data quickly.

👉 Example:

Scraping product prices from Amazon
Extracting news headlines from a website
📌 2. Why Use Python for Web Scraping?
Easy syntax and readability
Powerful libraries
Fast development
Popular Libraries:
BeautifulSoup → HTML parsing
requests → Send HTTP requests
Selenium → Dynamic websites
Scrapy → Large-scale scraping
📌 3. How Web Scraping Works
Send a request to a webpage
Get HTML content
Parse HTML
Extract required data
Store data (CSV, DB, JSON)
